      BoxGrinder is an open-source project so we make it easy to ask
      questions or contribute.

      ## Forums

      In our JBoss Community Portal anyone with a JBoss Community account
      can [start a discussion](http://community.jboss.org/en/boxgrinder?view=discussions) about BoxGrinder.

      * <http://community.jboss.org/en/boxgrinder?view=discussions>

      ## Issue Tracker

      We use JIRA to track bugs and feature requests. To submit a bug or
      feature request or to comment on an existing issue, you'll first
      need to [signup][jboss_signup] for a JBoss Community account.

      [jboss_signup]: https://community.jboss.org/login.jspa

      [![BoxGrinder Build issue tracker][bgbuild_small]](https://jira.jboss.org/browse/BGBUILD)
      [![BoxGrinder REST issue tracker][bgrest_small]](https://jira.jboss.org/browse/BGREST)

      ## IRC

      The developers and users of BoxGrinder hang out on the `#boxgrinder`
      channel on FreeNode.

      * [irc://irc.freenode.net/boxgrinder](irc://irc.freenode.net/boxgrinder)


